Package: biocpkgs
Title: Learning about Bioconductor packages
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: person("Laurent", "Gatto",
                  email = "lg390@cam.ac.uk",
		  role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: The package provides utiliites to detrieve and inspect
             the download stats for any Bioconductor package and to
	     calculate and visualise dependencies between packages.	     
Depends: R (>= 3.4.0)
Imports: readr, lubridate, pkgDepTools
Suggests: Rgraphviz
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Suggests: testthat
RoxygenNote: 6.0.1
